{"tid":2104032,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"初選仲有一日，投完票的人幫手做勢繼續宣傳","createTime":"2020-07-11T15:37:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-11T15:42:23.000Z","uid":94771,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"96b16fb41c47acac73b20d60d023a99441b5c20b","tid":2104032,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T15:37:05.000Z","msg":"選舉氣氛好重要架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好睇小你地做的野<br />\n可能做的野微不足道，但可能影響大局<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span class=\"x-large\">冷氣戰線</span></ins></strong><br />\n重現616宣傳攻勢，將自己所有FACEBOOK，IG，Twitter，Google頭像換成71文宣<br />\n<br />\nEXAMPLE :<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Facebook : </ins></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F1tq3rS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF1tq3rS.png&h=d56f25de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><ins>IG : </ins></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HGoOgNK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHGoOgNK.png&h=d4d7c585&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><ins>Twitter : </ins></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MAjhUzt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMAjhUzt.png&h=84a31b7b&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<strong><ins>Reddit : </ins></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cHwHmeJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcHwHmeJ.png&h=89f8512d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n再進一步<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">而FB同YT，<strong><ins>可以係<span class=\"gold\">直播，新聞PAGE</span>入面留言叫大家71見</ins></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><ins><strong><span class=\"gold\">除佐冷氣戰線，之外重有另一條戰線要繼續宣傳</span></strong></ins></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https://na.cx/i/2XXCE6p.png&amp;h=cd276ff3&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n<br />\n日期：7月9日 (四) 至 7月12日 (日)<br />\n時間：不限<br />\n地點：全港十八區<br />\n<br />\n<ins>再詳細參考方法</ins><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"orange\">藍屍因為連儂牆開花而疲於奔命<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/artxbGU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/artxbGU</a><br />\n#行動 #最新任務</span><br />\n<br />\n提供幾張好有用的初選文宣<br />\n你鐘意寫字又得，拎去做底印文宣都得<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C7dbeAo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC7dbeAo.jpg&h=c66c9f6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dWA81fo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdWA81fo.jpg&h=2cda773a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B4YB98J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB4YB98J.jpg&h=a40dd593&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OrawY14.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOrawY14.jpg&h=81197d93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6d4BqG4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6d4BqG4.jpg&h=f3147ba8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E6%B4%BE%E5%88%9D%E9%81%B8-251-%E7%A5%A8%E7%AB%99%E4%BD%8D%E7%BD%AE%E8%B3%87%E6%96%99%E4%B8%80%E8%A6%BD-%E5%91%A8%E6%9C%AB%E6%94%9C%E8%BA%AB%E4%BB%BD%E8%AD%89-%E5%9C%B0%E5%9D%80%E8%AD%89%E6%98%8E%E5%8F%AF%E6%8A%95%E7%A5%A8/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25B0%2591%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E5%2588%259D%25E9%2581%25B8-251-%25E7%25A5%25A8%25E7%25AB%2599%25E4%25BD%258D%25E7%25BD%25AE%25E8%25B3%2587%25E6%2596%2599%25E4%25B8%2580%25E8%25A6%25BD-%25E5%2591%25A8%25E6%259C%25AB%25E6%2594%259C%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E4%25BB%25BD%25E8%25AD%2589-%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%259D%2580%25E8%25AD%2589%25E6%2598%258E%25E5%258F%25AF%25E6%258A%2595%25E7%25A5%25A8%2F&d=GdzNT1%2FdEV%2FiwqmWSoLNng%2BnBs0jvEEXkL0KxwFTSeM%3D&h=3de7f94d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25B0%2591%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E5%2588%259D%25E9%2581%25B8-251-%25E7%25A5%25A8%25E7%25AB%2599%25E4%25BD%258D%25E7%25BD%25AE%25E8%25B3%2587%25E6%2596%2599%25E4%25B8%2580%25E8%25A6%25BD-%25E5%2591%25A8%25E6%259C%25AB%25E6%2594%259C%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E4%25BB%25BD%25E8%25AD%2589-%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%259D%2580%25E8%25AD%2589%25E6%2598%258E%25E5%258F%25AF%25E6%258A%2595%25E7%25A5%25A8%2F&h=c3777059\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E6%B4%BE%E5%88%9D%E9%81%B8-251-%E7%A5%A8%E7%AB%99%E4%BD%8D%E7%BD%AE%E8%B3%87%E6%96%99%E4%B8%80%E8%A6%BD-%E5%91%A8%E6%9C%AB%E6%94%9C%E8%BA%AB%E4%BB%BD%E8%AD%89-%E5%9C%B0%E5%9D%80%E8%AD%89%E6%98%8E%E5%8F%AF%E6%8A%95%E7%A5%A8/</a>"},{"pid":"0de69a2290cfcd2b5a8d7d61cc7eec071df92d02","tid":2104032,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T15:37:08.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><ins>現實戰線</ins></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2XXCE6p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2XXCE6p.png&h=cd276ff3&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n日期：7月9日 (四) 至 7月12日 (日)<br />\n時間：不限<br />\n地點：全港十八區<br />\n<br />\n<strong>現時推薦戰術<br />\n<ins>一擊脫離，觀察周圍環境</strong></ins><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WHXCE6Z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWHXCE6Z.png&h=19e856f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><strong><ins>＊唔好睇小依個戰術，好多小屋邨，私人屋苑推動選舉消失就係靠佢地＊</ins></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>快閃文宣，其實以狗力來講係好難處理架啦<br />\n佢地得幾種方法<br />\n1. <ins>叫藍屍盡量篤灰，再查CCTV咬幾個製做寒蟬效應</ins><br />\n2. <ins>係各區快閃熱點搵便衣狗仔伏人<br />\n</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"orange\">基本上得行運式拉人，如果小心Ｄ，貼完就走係好難捉到你<br />\n第二，如果全港有幾萬人/幾十萬人做，黑警唔會夠Workload一個一個貼快閃文宣查，相反如果少人做，黑警就可以一個一個Target，得閒就會查。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eiYzQxS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeiYzQxS.jpg&h=affd975e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins>一於去買一疊A4 size label周圍貼! 文宣都可以遍地開花, 等政府同藍絲都清唔晒!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每個人都唔需要貼得多，當每個人做兩張。<br />\n一個人就兩張，兩個就四張，四個就八張，一千個人就兩千張<br />\n如果有兩萬人做，全香港都係<strong><span class=\"orange\">快閃</span></strong>831文宣無咩難度<br />\n<span class=\"red\">係睇大家真係會唔會Take action咁解</span><br />\n</ins><br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\"><strong><span class=\"x-large\">低風險 低門檻 低成本<br />\n唔使再因為冇膽玩噴膠 怕俾人報串而做唔到文宣</span></strong></p><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TH2tr0q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTH2tr0q.jpg&h=86093f0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>一般文具舖都有! 預100蚊100張</ins></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gGj9UyA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgGj9UyA.jpg&h=0b180dc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins>再詳細參考方法</ins><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"orange\">藍屍因為連儂牆開花而疲於奔命<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/artxbGU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/artxbGU</a><br />\n#行動 #最新任務</span><br />\n<br />\n你鐘意寫字又得，拎去做底印文宣都得<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>我希望個日全港，唔同的地方都有文宣</strong></ins><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wahLaQg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwahLaQg.jpg&h=7a57ac81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/32Ud4ah.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F32Ud4ah.jpg&h=88f749de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m6rzOBX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm6rzOBX.jpg&h=04eff39b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dca78e6d924e3c3b9492f04a76b87c198b074928","tid":2104032,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T15:37:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6e4d76296702d6832f9d7055a4